<subSubSection id="2BF24ACA1F7CFF87FFEBFA8CFCF03236" pageId="55" pageNumber="334" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="635719411F7CFF87FFEBFA8CFEBA3682" blockId="55.[111,649,1389,1700]" box="[113,272,1389,1415]" pageId="55" pageNumber="334">OBSERVATIONS</paragraph>
<paragraph id="635719411F7CFF87FFEBFA6DFD8235A4" blockId="55.[111,649,1389,1700]" pageId="55" pageNumber="334">
<taxonomicName id="A4E862C21F7CFF87FFEBFA6DFE2136A1" authority="Schmid, 2012" authorityName="M. Schmid" authorityYear="2012" box="[113,395,1420,1446]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Primulaceae" genus="Tapeinosperma" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ericales" pageId="55" pageNumber="334" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="poueboense" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis id="519CC5531F7CFF87FFEBFA6DFE2136A1" box="[113,395,1420,1446]" italics="true" pageId="55" pageNumber="334">Tapeinosperma poueboense</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="4AAF78281F7CFF87FE0EFA6DFE4336A1" box="[404,489,1420,1446]" pageId="55" pageNumber="334" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
est proche de 
<taxonomicName id="A4E862C21F7CFF87FFE9FA4DFF4636C2" box="[115,236,1451,1477]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Primulaceae" genus="Tapeinosperma" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ericales" pageId="55" pageNumber="334" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="robustum">
<emphasis id="519CC5531F7CFF87FFE9FA4DFF4636C2" box="[115,236,1451,1477]" italics="true" pageId="55" pageNumber="334">T. robustum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, dont il se distingue principalement par ses fleurs sessiles ou presque. Sa distribution paraît limitée à la cordillère micaschisteuse allant de la région de Hienghène (Ton-non) à celle de Pouébo (Panié, Ignambi, Mandjélia), où il serait assez commun en forêt entre 500 et 
<quantity id="A410B4A41F7CFF87FE11F9ABFE483563" box="[395,482,1610,1636]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.2" pageId="55" pageNumber="334" unit="m" value="1200.0">1200 m</quantity>
, alors que l’aire de 
<taxonomicName id="A4E862C21F7CFF87FF08F98BFEBA3584" box="[146,272,1641,1667]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Primulaceae" genus="Tapeinosperma" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ericales" pageId="55" pageNumber="334" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="robustum">
<emphasis id="519CC5531F7CFF87FF08F98BFEBA3584" box="[146,272,1641,1667]" italics="true" pageId="55" pageNumber="334">T. robustum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
s’étend dans le sud et l’ouest de la Grande Terre, sur terrains ultramafiques.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="635719411F7CFF87FD21FF39FCF03236" blockId="55.[675,1209,216,305]" pageId="55" pageNumber="334">Se trouvant dans une zone protégée, sans intérêt minier ni agricole, l’espèce ne semble pas actuellement menacée.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
